---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Disclaimer"
  description="Legal disclaimer for FinePrintDecoder."
>
  <div class="container page-content prose">
    <h1>Disclaimer</h1>

    <p>
      FinePrintDecoder provides plain-English summaries of publicly available policies and
      agreements for informational purposes only. Read this page before relying on any
      summary you find here.
    </p>

    <h2>This is not legal advice</h2>
    <p>
      Nothing on this site is legal advice. The summaries are general descriptions of what a
      policy says, written for a general audience. They do not address the facts of any
      specific situation, and they do not account for jurisdictional variations, recent legal
      developments, or the particular terms of any modified or supplemental agreement that
      might apply to you.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you need to know how a policy applies to your specific circumstances, consult a
      licensed attorney in your jurisdiction.
    </p>

    <h2>No attorney-client relationship</h2>
    <p>
      Reading this site, contacting us through this site, or using any of the information
      published here does not create an attorney-client relationship. Communications sent to
      us through the contact form or any email address listed on the site are not
      confidential and are not subject to attorney-client privilege.
    </p>

    <h2>Accuracy and currency</h2>
    <p>
      We make a real effort to summarize policies accurately and to verify them against the
      source documents. Every summary shows when it was last verified. But:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Companies change their terms without notice. A summary may not reflect the current version.</li>
      <li>We are summarizing, not reproducing. Some nuance is unavoidably lost in translation.</li>
      <li>We can be wrong. If you spot an error, tell us — but verify against the company's official document before relying on anything you read here.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Always refer to the original document</h2>
    <p>
      Every summary on this site links to the company's authoritative source document. The
      company's actual policy is the binding agreement. Our summary is a tool for
      understanding it; it is not a substitute for it.
    </p>

    <h2>No affiliation</h2>
    <p>
      We are not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by any of the companies whose
      policies we summarize. Any company name, trademark, or product name mentioned on this
      site belongs to its respective owner. We mention them as a matter of fair comment on
      publicly available documents.
    </p>

    <h2>Affiliate disclosure</h2>
    <p>
      Some links on this site may be affiliate links — meaning we earn a small commission if
      you click and complete a purchase. Affiliate links never affect our editorial judgment
      about a policy, and we mark them as such where they appear.
    </p>

    <h2>AI involvement</h2>
    <p>
      Summaries on this site are produced with substantial AI assistance and reviewed by a
      human before publication. AI is good at reading long documents carefully and writing
      consistently structured summaries. It is also capable of being wrong. We treat the
      review pass as a serious editorial step, but you should still verify anything that
      matters against the source.
    </p>

    <h2>Limitation of liability</h2>
    <p>
      Use of this site is at your own risk. To the fullest extent permitted by law,
      FinePrintDecoder and its operators disclaim all warranties and shall not be liable for
      any damages — direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or otherwise — arising from
      your use of, or reliance on, the information on this site.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes to this disclaimer</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this disclaimer over time. Material changes will be noted at the top of
      the page along with the effective date.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
